*一句话：** 引擎只声明「要什么 / 存什么」的 Port 协议；具体落盘由外部 IO 模块响应。本机默认实现物理落在 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. 为什么拆\\n\\n引擎是纯领域逻辑，将来可嵌入：\\n\\n| 宿主 | IO 形态（示例） |\\n|------|-----------------|\\n| Studio V2 / 本机 Next | `engineIOModule`：JSON+fs + SQLite + jsonl |\\n| 电话机壳 | 设备私有存储 / 只读 Content 包 |\\n| 纯浏览器 | **不本地 IO**；经 XHR→后端再落盘 |\\n\\n存储方案随平台变；**剧情与会话规则不变**。故：程序上 Port 化，物理上 IO 实现离开 `packages/rpg-engine`。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2. 拓扑\\n\\n```text\\nBrowser（仅意图与展示）\\n  ↓ XHR\\nNext  [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":53,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-a3f88c1b-623b-48d0-bf27-96dc19775234-6\\nfc_a3f3dfaf-890e-9d3e-924e-9618026d56b6_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"globToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"targetDirectory\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2\",\"globPattern\":\"**/engineIOModule/**/*\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2\",\"files\":[\"engineIOModule/content/contentReads.ts\",\"tests/engineIOModule/fsContentPort.test.ts\",\"engineIOModule/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/log/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/createEngineIOPorts.ts\",\"tests/engineIOModule/fsEngineLogPort.test.ts\",\"engineIOModule/log/fsEngineLogPort.ts\",\"engineIOModule/content/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/content/fsContentPort.ts\",\"engineIOModule/content/workspaceSnapshot.ts\",\"tests/engineIOModule/fsProfilePort.test.ts\",\"engineIOModule/profile/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/profile/fsProfilePort.ts\",\"engineIOModule/memory/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/memory/sqliteMemoryPort.ts\",\"engineIOMod [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":54,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-a3f88c1b-623b-48d0-bf27-96dc19775234-7\\nfc_a3f3dfaf-890e-9d3e-924e-9618026d56b6_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"createEngineHost|e