\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-b253af3b-5cab-47a2-a278-e7044b561bfc-37\\nfc_30a2314b-1dd5-9557-9ca0-31cb1b2b21cd_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"utils/server|Host|engine\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md\",\"glob\":\"*.md\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-b253af3b-5cab-47a2-a278-e7044b561bfc-37\\nfc_30a2314b-1dd5-9557-9ca0-31cb1b2b21cd_1\",\"offset\":0},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"utils/server|Host|engine\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md\",\"outputMode\":\"content\",\"workspaceResults\":{\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\":{\"content\":{\"matches\":[{\"file\":\"docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":30,\"content\":\"  engineIOModule/   # Server-only：本机引擎 Port IO（禁止 Client 引用）\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":358,\"content\": [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":243,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-b253af3b-5cab-47a2-a278-e7044b561bfc-38\\nfc_30a2314b-1dd5-9557-9ca0-31cb1b2b21cd_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":120},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# Studio V2 前端目录结构与落点规则\\n\\n> 本文是 Studio V2 前端目录结构的真源。  \\n> 目的不是追求抽象优雅，而是让人类、Cursor、批执行器和门禁脚本都能一眼判断：一个文件应该放在哪里，不应该放在哪里。\\n\\n## 1. 为什么需要这份规则\\n\\nStudio V2 第一阶段是静态页重构，不要求真实保存、真实调试或真实导入导出闭环。\\n\\n但静态阶段也必须保证代码地基不歪。如果目录边界不清晰，AI 会自然出现以下退化：\\n\\n- 先平铺文件，再为了过门禁移动到子目录。\\n- 移动后保留兼容转发文件，导致父目录和子目录长期并存。\\n- `features`、`domain`、`services` 被不同执行者解释成不同含义。\\n- 页面组件、业务编排、mock 数据、类型契约混在一起。\\n- 后续真实功能接入时，只能在已经歪掉的结构上继续堆。\\n\\n因此 Studio V2 从此只认固定目录结构。任何新增、迁移、修复任务都必须先判断目标文件属于哪一类，再落到对应目录。\\n\\n## 2. 顶层结构\\n\\nStudio V2 前端只认以下顶层业务目录：\\n\\n```text\\napps/studioV2/\\n  app/\\n  src/\\n  typeFiles/\\n  tests/\\n  engineIOModule/   # Server-only：本机引擎 Port IO（禁止 Client 引用）\\n```\\n\\n其它顶层业务目录默认禁止。\\n\\n允许的工程目录包括： [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":276,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-6dc6b81c-3a8e-4514-8899-8ab582959923-45\\nfc_556fc1f5-7dba-9905-8289-578ab6c035db_4\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/18-部署拓扑与BS架构.md\",\"limit\":80},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# 18. 部署拓扑 · B/S 与持久化\\n\\n相关：[05](./05-技术选型与工程边界.md) · [19](./19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) · [21](./21-Studio客户端分层.md) · [50](../需求/50-对话与模型适配.md) · [10](../需求/10-用户与存档.md)\\n\\n## 1. 产品形态\\n\\n```text\\nBrowser (React + MUI + scss module + Zustand/bis/shell)\\n  · 故事列表 / 画布投影 / 调试 UI / UserGate\\n        ↓ HTTP / SSE\\nNext.js — API 门面\\n  · 开发态 userId（无密码）\\n  · DTO、错误码（见 19 §15）\\n  · 调用 EngineHost 单例；决定何时 save\\n        ↓\\npackages/rpg-engine — EngineHost\\n  · CallSession / Resolver / Exit / Effect / FreePipeline\\n  · 经 **存取 Port** 访问 Content / 薄 Profile / Memory / 日志（协议见 [23](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)）\\n  · 不内置 fs/sqlite 实现；本机实现见 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule\\n```\\n\\nStudio 客户端分层见 [21](./21-Studio客户端分层.md)。\\n\\n [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":280,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" engineIOModule ports\",\"session_id\":\"a3680f7e-0b6d-44a0-bebb-f72e7a9829f8\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784776839}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":385,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nReload placement needs to be decided between the write functions themselves and the API routes. The character write and delete APIs will also be wired to reload. The engineIOModule README comment for createEngineIOPorts will be updated.\",\"session_id\":\"a3680f7e-0b6d-44a0-bebb-f72e7a9829f8\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784785551}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":395,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-e8588bd7-3181-4e5e-bc5e-f6536373bb10-50\\nfc_a12b6caf-718f-9f08-b53e-2f9455d44e8c_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/tests/engineIOModule/fsProfilePort.test.ts\",\"limit\":40}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-e8588bd7-3181-4e5e-bc5e-f6536373bb10-50\\nfc_a12b6caf-718f-9f08-b53e-2f9455d44e8c_3\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784784785571\"},\"model_call_id\":\"51f4eeec-4abc-4338-82b6-7ffa26490294-10-hk0v\",\"session_id\":\"a3680f7e-0b6d-44a0-bebb-f72e7a9829f8\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784785558}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":396,"content":"[gbx] · 读取 apps/studioV2/tests/engineIOModule/fsProfilePort.test.ts","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":405,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-e8588bd7-3181-4e5e-bc5e-f6536373bb10-50\\nfc_a12b6caf-718f-9f08-b53e-2f9455d44e8c_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/tests/engineIOModule/fsProfilePort.test.ts\",\"limit\":40},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"/**\\n * 模块名称：engineIOModule FsProfilePort 验收测（自引擎迁出后）\\n */\\nimport { mkdtemp, readFile, rm, writeFile, mkdir } from \\\"node:fs/promises\\\";\\nimport os from \\\"node:os\\\";\\nimport path from \\\"node:path\\\";\\nimport { afterEach, describe, expect, it } from \\\"vitest\\\";\\nimport { isEngineError, PlayerProfileSchema } from \\\"@airpc/rpg-engine\\\";\\n// 引用了本机 Fs Profile 工厂，用于验收迁出后的读写行为等价\\nimport { createFsProfilePort } from \\\"../../engineIOModule/profile/fsProfilePort\\\";\\n\\ndescribe(\\\"FsProfilePort\\\", () => {\\n\\