son`。**Batch 7 / V2-IO-8 审查结果：pass**（`blocker=0`，`critical=0`）\\n\\n已写入 `.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports/reviews/latest.json`。\\n\\n要点：\\n- `validatePackage` / `validateReferencedAgents` 已去掉 `node:fs`，规则只消费 `PackageValidateBundle` + `ContentPort`\\n- Host / Studio server 经 `loadPackageForValidate` 装包；Client 未引用 `engineIOModule`\\n- 执行索引 V2-IO-8 已 ✅；executor 末态 `quality:engine` 绿（含搬迁后），rebuild 后 `quality:studio` 绿\\n- 仅 1 条 **minor**：`confRaw`/`cardRaw`/`diskCardIds` 待 V2-IO-11 回写技术设计 23\\n\\n建议下一状态：`VERIFY_BATCH`\", [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":626,"content":"- Host / Studio server 经 `loadPackageForValidate` 装包；Client 未引用 `engineIOModule`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"./.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports/prompts/prompt-1784784565510.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":36,"content":"blocker：引擎仍直 fs/sqlite 实现、无注入、engineIOModule 进 Client、行为不等价、文档未回写、quality 红。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"./.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports/prompts/agent-1784784123374.log","matches":[{"lineNumber":12,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-c29cac59-1efb-491c-9178-db5e817b78dc-0\\nfc_e6eae36d-02ff-9000-904f-9ad1dc144cd2_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports/prompts/prompt-1784784123374.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"You are the EXECUTOR for general-batch-exe.\\n\\nWorkdir: /Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\\nExecution index (--exFile): /Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_执行索引.md\\nWorkflow dir: /Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports\\nCurrent batch number: 7\\nActive task IDs: V2-IO-8\\nReview run ID: (not a review role)\\n\\nMust read first (relative to workdir):\\n- AGENTS.md\\n- .cursor/rules/codingRole.mdc\\n- .cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\\n- .cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc\\n- .cursor/rules/studio-v2-client-server-isolation.mdc\\n- .cursor/rules/studio-v2-quality.mdc\\n- .cursor/rules/testing-and-quality.mdc\\n- . [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":35,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-11bc799b-90ad-446c-8b52-db2b15230cc4-2\\nfc_e7b47b14-1d56-92a9-9788-b949b3a9cbad_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_执行索引.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\n# Studio V2.0 · 引擎存取 Port 抽象执行索引（gbx / general-batch-exe）\\n# 用法：node .cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile <本文件> --workdir <仓库根> [--dry-run]\\n# 本轮目标：引擎存取 Port 协议落地 + 现网 IO 迁入 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule + Host 注入装配 + 文档收口\\nbatch_size: 1\\nmax_rounds: 80\\nmax_fix_attempts: 5\\nmax_ineffective_fixes: 2\\nstop_on_fail: true\\ngroup: order\\n\\nverify_default:\\n  - npm run quality:engine\\n  - npm run quality:studio\\n\\nread_first:\\n  - AGENTS.md\\n  - .cursor/rules/codingRole.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/studio-v2-client-server-isolation.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/studio-v2-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/testing- [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":36,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-11bc799b-90ad-446c-8b52-db2b15230cc4-4\\nfc_e7b47b14-1d56-92a9-9788-b949b3a9cbad_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\ndescription: packages/rpg-engine 纯引擎边界\\nglobs: packages/rpg-engine/**\\nalwaysApply: false\\n---\\n\\n# 引擎包边界（rpg-engine）\\n\\n详情：[05](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/05-技术选型与工程边界.md)、[19](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)、[02](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md)。\\n\\n## 必须执行\\n\\n- **禁止** import：`react`、`react-dom`、`next`、`@xyflow/*`。\\n- **禁止** `window` / `document` / `localStorage`（测试可注入）。\\n- **EngineHost 单例**由 server/壳持有；本包提供 create/host API。\\n- **CallSession** 在 Host 内存；`frozenCard`；同 user 通话互斥。\\n- Composer 只读；EffectExecutor 仅出口/Free 管线；工具只登记 candidate。\\n- **FreeCallPostPipeline** 为 Free 挂机唯一总入口（可注入）；v1 = 有效门闩 + MemoryCommit +（有 candidate 则 ExitSelector）；禁 transcript 隐式扫描。\\n- Free Session.`packageId = [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":54,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-0b6bf26f-7f28-459d-b809-7751cdf292e3-9\\nfc_5152aa0c-1657-9fa0-aa3b-3ad041e8903f_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"globToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"targetDirectory\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2\",\"globPattern\":\"**/engineIOModule/**/*\"}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-0b6bf26f-7f28-459d-b809-7751cdf292e3-9\\nfc_5152aa0c-1657-9fa0-aa3b-3ad041e8903f_3\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784784141203\"},\"model_call_id\":\"7d5a523f-ae64-455e-b049-3e18d53be39c-2-8arb\",\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784141129}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":59,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-0b6bf26f-7f28-459d-b809-7751cdf292e3-9\\nfc_5152aa0c-1657-9fa0-aa3b-3ad041e8903f_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"globToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"targetDirectory\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2\",\"globPattern\":\"**/engineIOModule/**/*\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2\",\"files\":[\"tests/engineIOModule/fsContentPort.test.ts\",\"engineIOModule/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/log/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/createEngineIOPorts.ts\",\"tests/engineIOModule/fsEngineLogPort.test.ts\",\"engineIOModule/log/fsEngineLogPort.ts\",\"engineIOModule/content/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/content/fsContentPort.ts\",\"engineIOModule/content/contentReads.ts\",\"engineIOModule/content/workspaceSnapshot.ts\",\"tests/engineIOModule/fsProfilePort.test.ts\",\"engineIOModule/profile/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/profile/fsProfilePort.ts\",\"engineIOModule/memory/README.md\",\"engineIOModule/memory/sqliteMemoryPort.ts\",\"engineIOMod [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":60,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-0b6bf26f-7f28-459d-b809-7751cdf292e3-10\\nfc_5152aa0c-1657-9fa0-aa3b-3ad041e8903f_4\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"ContentPort|contentPort|validatePackage|readFile|node:fs\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-0b6bf26f-7f28-459d-b809-7751cdf292e3-10\\nfc_5152aa0c-1657-9fa0-aa3b-3ad041e8903f_4\",\"offset\":0},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"ContentPort|contentPort|validatePackage|readFile|node:fs\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine\",\"outputMode\":\"content\",\"workspaceResults\":{\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\":{\"content\":{\"matches\":[{\"file\":\"packages/rpg-engine/src/host/createEngineHost.ts\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":58,\"content\":\"  validatePackage as runValidatePackage,\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":59,\"content\":\"} from \\\"../validation/validatePackage.js\\\";\",\"co [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":63,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" Checking engineIOModule\",\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784145296}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":72,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-75be121f-e372-4a35-903f-69e3fc2c543a-13\\nfc_6df00686-a1d3-9617-b9e6-3bb66c67eff3_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/content/fsContentPort.ts\"}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-75be121f-e372-4a35-903f-69e3fc2c543a-13\\nfc_6df00686-a1d3-9617-b9e6-3bb66c67eff3_2\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784784145369\"},\"model_call_id\":\"7d5a523f-ae64-455e-b049-3e18d53be39c-3-n4rv\",\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784145300}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":73,"content":"[gbx] · 读取 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/content/fsContentPort.ts","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":81,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-75be121f-e372-4a35-903f-69e3fc2c543a-12\\nfc_6df00686-a1d3-9617-b9e6-3bb66c67eff3_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md\",\"offset\":173,\"limit\":220},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"### 4.3 ContentPort\\n\\n**职责：** Content 只读热路径（工作区快照、按需读卡、校验装包、资产 meta 探测）。  \\n**不负责：** Studio 画布 layout 编辑写盘、资源二进制上传（可仍走 BFF）；但 validate 需要的 **读** 必须能经本 Port 完成。  \\n**本机实现：** 扫 `workspace.json` / `storis-packages` / `characters` 等（布局见 [19 §3](./19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)）。\\n\\n```ts\\n/** loadWorkspace 后 Host 内存缓存所需最小快照（不含预读全部故事卡正文） */\\ninterface WorkspaceSnapshot {\\n  /** 逻辑工作区键；本机即 dataRoot 绝对/相对路径字符串 */\\n  workspaceKey: string;\\n  /** packageId → conf；cards 映射可为空，按需 loadCard 再填 */\\n  packages: Array<{\\n    packageId: string;\\n    conf: StoryPackageConf;\\n    /** 实现私有定位提示（本机可为目录绝对路径）；引擎不当作公共 API 依赖 */\\n    packageLocator?: string;\\n  }>;\\n  characters: CharacterDef[];           // [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":82,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-75be121f-e372-4a35-903f-69e3fc2c543a-13\\nfc_6df00686-a1d3-9617-b9e6-3bb66c67eff3_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/content/fsContentPort.ts\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"/**\\n\\t* 模块名称：本机 Fs ContentPort\\n\\t* 模块说明：自 packages/rpg-engine loadWorkspace fs 扫描迁出；\\n\\t* 路径仅本模块知道（storis-packages / characters / assets）。\\n\\t* Server 边界：仅 Host 装配 / API / *.server.ts 可引用；禁止 Client。\\n\\t* 协议：技术设计 23 §4.3。\\n\\t*/\\nimport type { ContentPort } from \\\"@airpc/rpg-engine\\\";\\n// 引用了 Workspace 快照读盘，用于 loadWorkspaceSnapshot\\nimport { loadWorkspaceSnapshotFromFs } from \\\"./workspaceSnapshot\\\";\\n// 引用了按需读卡/conf/资产/validate bundle，用于 ContentPort 其余方法\\nimport {\\n\\tassetMetaExistsFromFs,\\n\\tassetUriExistsFromFs,\\n\\tloadPackageForValidateFromFs,\\n\\treadAssetMetaFromFs,\\n\\treadCardFromFs,\\n\\treadPackageConfFromFs,\\n} from \\\"./contentReads\\\";\\n\\n/**\\n\\t* 创建本机 ContentPort（行为与迁前 H [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":84,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-75be121f-e372-4a35-903f-69e3fc2c543a-14\\nfc_6df00686-a1d3-9617-b9e6-3bb66c67eff3_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/tests/helpers/fsContentPort.ts\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"/**\\n * 模块名称：测试用 Fs ContentPort\\n * 模块说明：与 engineIOModule/content 行为对齐的测试镜像；\\n * 引擎测不得 import apps/studioV2（独立性优先于 DRY）。\\n */\\nimport type { ContentPort } from \\\"../../src/ports/contentPort.js\\\";\\n// 引用了 Workspace 快照读盘，用于 loadWorkspaceSnapshot\\nimport { loadWorkspaceSnapshotFromFs } from \\\"./content/workspaceSnapshot.js\\\";\\n// 引用了按需读卡/conf/资产/validate bundle\\nimport {\\n\\tassetMetaExistsFromFs,\\n\\tassetUriExistsFromFs,\\n\\tloadPackageForValidateFromFs,\\n\\treadAssetMetaFromFs,\\n\\treadCardFromFs,