xtLine":false},{"lineNumber":85,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-12\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/createEngineIOPorts.ts\"}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-12\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_1\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784781457623\"},\"model_call_id\":\"2310601a-1e8e-4d84-91ad-c4a6d394ccba-3-b797\",\"session_id\":\"d63bd641-12cd-4e19-ad56-02438074c485\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784781457623}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":86,"content":"[gbx] · 读取 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/createEngineIOPorts.ts","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":93,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-16\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_5\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"engineIOModule\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/scripts/studio-quality\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-16\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_5\",\"offset\":0}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-16\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_5\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784781457797\"},\"model_call_id\":\"2310601a-1e8e-4d84-91ad-c4a6d394ccba-3-b797\",\"session_id\":\"d63bd641-12cd-4e19-ad56-02438074c485\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784781457774}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":94,"content":"[gbx] · 搜索 engineIOModule in scripts/studio-quality","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":96,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-11\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/README.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# engineIOModule · 本机引擎存取 IO\\n\\n> **Server 区专用。** 禁止 `pageComponents` / `bis` / `stores` / `commonUiComponents` / `ajaxProxy` / `typeFiles` 及任何 `\\\"use client\\\"` 模块引用本目录。  \\n> 协议真源：[技术设计 23](../../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。  \\n> 需求：[引擎存取Port抽象_需求.md](../../../docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_需求.md)。\\n\\n## 职责\\n\\n本目录承载 **Studio V2 本机** 对引擎 Port 的 IO 实现（JSON+fs / SQLite / jsonl）。  \\n引擎只声明 Port；**不** import 本模块。装配发生在 Next API / Host 单例处：`createEngineIOPorts(dataRoot)` → `createEngineHost({ ...ports })`。\\n\\n## 目录\\n\\n```text\\nengineIOModule/\\n  content/                 # ContentPort：Workspace / 包 / 角色 / 资产 meta 读（V2-IO-6）\\n  profile/                 # ProfilePort：薄 Profile 读写（V2-IO-5）\\n [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":97,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-12\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/createEngineIOPorts.ts\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"/**\\n\\t* 模块名称：本机引擎 IO 装配工厂（骨架）\\n\\t* 模块说明：按 dataRoot 创建 Memory / Profile / Content / EngineLog Ports。\\n\\t* Server 边界：仅 app/api、Host 装配、*.server.ts、utils/server 可引用；\\n\\t* 禁止 Client（pageComponents / bis / stores / typeFiles / ajaxProxy 等）任何 import。\\n\\t* 实现迁入节奏见里程碑 V2-IO-4～V2-IO-7；本文件在 V2-IO-3 仅占位，避免误用未迁完的装配。\\n\\t*/\\nimport type {\\n\\tContentPort,\\n\\tEngineLogPort,\\n\\tMemoryPort,\\n\\tProfilePort,\\n} from \\\"@airpc/rpg-engine\\\";\\n\\n/** 本机 Studio 注入 Host 的四 Port 套件（技术设计 23）。 */\\nexport type EngineIOPorts = {\\n\\tmemory: MemoryPort;\\n\\tprofile: ProfilePort;\\n\\tcontent: ContentPort;\\n\\tengineLog: EngineLogPort;\\n};\\n\\n/**\\n\\t* 创建指向 `dataRoot` 的本机 Ports。\\n\\t* V2-IO-3 骨架阶段尚未迁入实现；调用方须等 V2-IO-4+ 完 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":98,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-13\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md\",\"offset\":350,\"limit\":60},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"\\n- **测试：** 注入内存假 Port。  \\n- **本机 Studio：** `engineIOModule` 工厂一次创建全套并注入。  \\n- **禁止**引擎在未注入时偷偷 `createSqliteMemoryPort(path.join(...))` 作为长期真源（迁完后删除该默认硬实现）。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 6. `engineIOModule` 物理约定\\n\\n路径：`apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`（名固定）。\\n\\n建议子目录（实现可微调）：\\n\\n```text\\nengineIOModule/\\n  content/     # Workspace / 包 / 角色 / 资产 meta 读\\n  profile/     # 薄 Profile 读写\\n  memory/      # Sqlite MemoryPort 实现\\n  log/         # jsonl\\n  createEngineIOPorts.ts  # 工厂：dataRoot → ports\\n```\\n\\n- 属 **Server 区**：仅 `app/api`、Host 装配、`*.server.ts` 可引用。  \\n- 现网技术不变：Content/Profile = JSON+fs；Memory = SQLite；Log = jsonl。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 7. validatePackage\\n\\n- **规则与报错形状**留在引擎（纯函数吃结构化输入）。  \\n- ** [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":100,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-17\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_6\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/content/README.md\"}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-17\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_6\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784781457934\"},\"model_call_id\":\"2310601a-1e8e-4d84-91ad-c4a6d394ccba-3-b797\",\"session_id\":\"d63bd641-12cd-4e19-ad56-02438074c485\",\